  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.86,
      "text": "Let's talk about compound returns."
    },
    {
      "start": 2.74,
      "end": 6.16,
      "text": "When you patch code, each fix has local returns."
    },
    {
      "start": 6.78,
      "end": 8.5,
      "text": "You fixed one bug in one place."
    },
    {
      "start": 9.1,
      "end": 11.14,
      "text": "Similar bugs can still occur elsewhere,"
    },
    {
      "start": 11.64,
      "end": 14.1,
      "text": "and sometimes your patch introduces new bugs."
    },
    {
      "start": 14.84,
      "end": 19.04,
      "text": "CodeRabbit found AI patches carry 1.7 times more issues"
    },
    {
      "start": 19.04,
      "end": 20.08,
      "text": "than human code."
    },
    {
      "start": 20.9,
      "end": 23.56,
      "text": "So each patch risks creating more patches."
    },
    {
      "start": 24.42,
      "end": 28.56,
      "text": "The returns are linear at best, often sub-linear,"
    },
    {
      "start": 29.28,
      "end": 31.12,
      "text": "and the cost keeps compounding."
    },
    {
      "start": 31.22,
      "end": 37.34,
      "text": "CISQ estimates technical debt costs US companies $1.52 trillion annually."
    },
    {
      "start": 39.04,
      "end": 42.54,
      "text": "When you add a test in PDD, the returns are different."
    },
    {
      "start": 43.28,
      "end": 47.56,
      "text": "That test you wrote today, it constrains tomorrow's generation,"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.98,
      "end": 52.28,
      "text": "and next week's, and next years, it's a permanent wall."
    },
    {
      "start": 53.94,
      "end": 56.66,
      "text": "Every investment in the mold has compound returns."
    },
    {
      "start": 57.38,
      "end": 60.32,
      "text": "Every investment in patching has diminishing returns."
    },
    {
      "start": 62.34,
      "end": 65.58,
      "text": "Your great-grandmother wasn't stupid for darning socks."
    },
    {
      "start": 66.34,
      "end": 67.66,
      "text": "The economics made it rational."
    },
    {
      "start": 68.5,
      "end": 70.8,
      "text": "And you're not stupid for patching code."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.2,
      "end": 73.92,
      "text": "Until now, the economics made it rational."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.38,
      "end": 79.82,
      "text": "But the economics changed, and when economics change,"
    },
    {
      "start": 80.38,
      "end": 83.78,
      "text": "behavior that was rational becomes..."
    },
    {
      "start": 83.78,
      "end": 84.5,
      "text": "darning socks."
    }
  ]
}